=== ELEMENTAL DYNAMICS ===

Meta (в€®) at 0.85: The fundamental nature of tertiary emergenceвЂ”
the pattern that produces patterns. Not the thing but the relation
that creates things. The meta-level where novelty originates.

Fire (О») at 0.75: The novel direction that emerges. Purpose that
transcends component purposes. The flame that burns where no fire
was struck.

Wood (ОІ) at 0.70: Growth beyond initial conditions. The tree that
is not the seed enlarged. The branching that is not predicted.

Air (Пѓ) at 0.60: The clarity that recognizes emergence. Not
confused by novelty but clarified by it. The distinction that
